---
/**
 * Print-optimized resume page for PDF generation
 * ATS-friendly: single-column, no graphics, standard headings
 * Excludes: About section, Projects section, oldest experience
 */
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Michael Funk - Resume</title>
    <style is:global>
      /* Reset and base styles */
      *,
      *::before,
      *::after {
        box-sizing: border-box;
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
      }

      html {
        font-size: 11pt;
        line-height: 1.4;
      }

      body {
        font-family: Arial, Helvetica, sans-serif;
        color: #000;
        background: #fff;
        max-width: 816px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        padding: 36px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      /* Header */
      .header {
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 0.3in;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        padding-bottom: 0.15in;
      }

      .name {
        font-size: 20pt;
        font-weight: bold;
        margin-bottom: 0.08in;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }

      .title {
        font-size: 11pt;
        color: #333;
        margin-bottom: 0.08in;
      }

      .contact {
        font-size: 10pt;
        color: #333;
      }

      .contact a {
        color: #333;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      .contact span {
        margin: 0 0.1in;
      }

      /* Section styles */
      .section {
        margin-bottom: 0.2in;
      }

      .section-title {
        font-size: 11pt;
        font-weight: bold;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #000;
        padding-bottom: 0.03in;
        margin-bottom: 0.1in;
        letter-spacing: 0.5px;
      }

      /* Summary */
      .summary {
        font-size: 10pt;
        line-height: 1.5;
      }

      /* Experience */
      .job {
        margin-bottom: 0.15in;
      }

      .job:last-child {
        margin-bottom: 0;
      }

      .job-header {
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: baseline;
        margin-bottom: 0.03in;
      }

      .job-title {
        font-weight: bold;
        font-size: 10.5pt;
      }

      .job-date {
        font-size: 10pt;
        color: #333;
      }

      .job-company {
        font-size: 10pt;
        font-style: italic;
        margin-bottom: 0.05in;
      }

      .job-achievements {
        list-style-type: disc;
        margin-left: 0.2in;
        font-size: 10pt;
      }

      .job-achievements li {
        margin-bottom: 0.03in;
      }

      /* Skills */
      .skills-grid {
        font-size: 10pt;
      }

      .skill-row {
        margin-bottom: 0.05in;
      }

      .skill-category {
        font-weight: bold;
        display: inline;
      }

      /* Education */
      .education-item {
        font-size: 10pt;
      }

      .education-school {
        font-weight: bold;
      }

      .education-degree {
        font-style: italic;
      }

      /* Print styles */
      @media print {
        html, body {
          width: 216mm; /* Letter width */
          height: 279mm; /* Letter height */
          font-size: 10.5pt;
          background: #fff;
          overflow: visible;
        }

        body {
          padding: 12.7mm; /* 0.5 inch margin */
          margin: 0;
          max-width: none;
        }

        @page {
          size: letter;
          margin: 0;
        }
      }

      /* Screen-only styles */
      @media screen {
        body {
          box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
          margin-top: 0.5in;
          margin-bottom: 0.5in;
        }

        .print-notice {
          position: fixed;
          top: 10px;
          right: 10px;
          background: #333;
          color: #fff;
          padding: 10px 15px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          font-size: 12px;
          cursor: pointer;
          z-index: 1000;
        }

        .print-notice:hover {
          background: #555;
        }
      }

      @media print {
        .print-notice {
          display: none;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <button class="print-notice" onclick="window.print()">
      Press Ctrl+P or click to print/save as PDF
    </button>

    <header class="header">
      <h1 class="name">MICHAEL FUNK</h1>
      <p class="title">Senior Software Engineer | Full Stack Developer</p>
      <p class="contact">
        <a href="mailto:funk-michael@outlook.com">funk-michael@outlook.com</a>
        <span>|</span>
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/michaelafunk">linkedin.com/in/michaelafunk</a>
        <span>|</span>
        <span>Sacramento, CA</span>
      </p>
    </header>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Professional Summary</h2>
      <p class="summary">
        Senior Software Engineer with 8+ years of experience building scalable web applications
        and leading technical initiatives. Expert in React, TypeScript, and modern JavaScript
        ecosystems with strong full-stack capabilities in .NET Core and cloud infrastructure.
        Proven track record of architecting monorepo strategies, establishing testing frameworks,
        and delivering high-impact features from concept to production.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Experience</h2>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-header">
          <span class="job-title">Senior Software Engineer II</span>
          <span class="job-date">June 2022 - Present</span>
        </div>
        <p class="job-company">Highlight, Remote</p>
        <ul class="job-achievements">
          <li>
            Architected monorepo strategy with Turborepo and pnpm workspaces, enabling atomic
            cross-package changes across 3+ applications and improving developer velocity
          </li>
          <li>
            Led full-stack development of consumer-facing application from POC to production,
            including onboarding flows, SMS verification, and mobile-optimized experiences
          </li>
          <li>
            Built analytics dashboard with interactive visualizations, cross-tabulation analysis,
            and export capabilities for market research teams
          </li>
          <li>
            Established API package architecture with RTK Query integrations, caching strategies,
