          </li>
          <li>
            Implemented testing and observability infrastructure with Playwright end-to-end (E2E)
            test suites, Datadog Real User Monitoring (RUM), and Amplitude analytics
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-header">
          <span class="job-title">Software Engineer</span>
          <span class="job-date">March 2019 - May 2022</span>
        </div>
        <p class="job-company">AVB Marketing, Remote</p>
        <ul class="job-achievements">
          <li>
            Migrated Create React App (CRA) to Next.js for platform serving 800+ e-commerce
