          </li>
          <li>
            Integrated third-party credit verification and payment providers, facilitating $9M+
            monthly revenue through checkout systems
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-header">
          <span class="job-title">Software Engineer</span>
          <span class="job-date">August 2018 - March 2019</span>
        </div>
        <p class="job-company">Intel Corporation, Folsom, CA</p>
        <ul class="job-achievements">
          <li>
            Developed internal test automation suite for NAND memory validation using Python and
            Django, improving testing efficiency and coverage
          </li>
          <li>
            Created comprehensive onboarding documentation for local development environment setup,
            reducing new developer ramp-up time
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="job">
        <div class="job-header">
          <span class="job-title">Software Developer II</span>
          <span class="job-date">December 2016 - June 2018</span>
        </div>
        <p class="job-company">Stanislaus County Agricultural Commissioner's Office, Modesto, CA</p>
        <ul class="job-achievements">
          <li>
            Built offline-capable Progressive Web Application (PWA) for field phytosanitary
            inspections on iPads, enabling data collection without network connectivity
          </li>
          <li>
            Developed web application for scale testing records with automated PDF generation for
            inspection certifications and invoices
          </li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Skills</h2>
      <div class="skills-grid">
        <div class="skill-row">
          <span class="skill-category">Languages:</span>
          TypeScript, JavaScript, C#, SQL, Python, HTML5, CSS3
        </div>
        <div class="skill-row">
          <span class="skill-category">Frontend:</span>
          React, Next.js, Redux, RTK Query, Tailwind CSS, Playwright, Testing Library, Responsive
          Design
        </div>
        <div class="skill-row">
          <span class="skill-category">Backend:</span>
          .NET Core, Node.js, RESTful APIs, Hono, tRPC, PostgreSQL, GraphQL
        </div>
        <div class="skill-row">
          <span class="skill-category">DevOps & Tools:</span>
          Docker, Kubernetes, Amazon Web Services (AWS), Turborepo, CI/CD, Nginx, Git, Datadog
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="section">
      <h2 class="section-title">Education</h2>
      <div class="education-item">
        <span class="education-school">California State University, Stanislaus</span>
        <br />
        <span class="education-degree"
          >Bachelor of Science in Business Administration - Accounting | Minor: Computer Science</span
        >
      </div>
    </section>

    <script>
      // Auto-trigger print dialog when page loads (optional - user can dismiss)
      if (window.location.search.includes("print=true")) {
        window.addEventListener("load", () => {
          setTimeout(() => window.print(), 500);
        });
      }
    </script>
  </body>
</html>
